            "type": "text",
            "text": "For API teams leveraging embedding models, performance benchmarking is critical to ensure scalability and efficiency. The BGE M3 model, optimized in FP16 precision, requires rigorous evaluation. A detailed bge m3 embedding benchmark helps identify optimal configurations for real-world API workloads."
          }
        ]
