            "type": "text",
            "text": "To deploy BGE M3 effectively: implement asynchronous endpoints to handle embedding requests, use batching to maximize GPU utilization, and monitor performance with tools like Prometheus. Cache frequent embeddings to reduce latency, and regularly re-run benchmarks after model updates or infrastructure changes to maintain efficiency."
